Elton John is celebrating a huge milestone – he is officially 29 years sober, According to  Justjared.com. “29 years ago today, I was a broken man. I finally summoned up the courage to say 3 words that would change my life: ‘I need help,’” Elton posted on his Instagram account. Powered by RubiQube Ad Network He continued, “Thank-you to all the selfless people who have helped me on my journey through sobriety. I am eternally grateful.” Elton also posted a photo of his 29 year chip he received for his sobriety journey. Congratulations to Elton John on this huge milestone.